 Creativity and ingenuity are revealed when all available resources are effectively used within the functional departments of an organization.
 The result of this is that the process of an organization that is working together to overcome an obstacle can lead to a new innovative process to meet the needs of the customer.
 To enable innovation in an organization, management must create a culture that fosters innovation, shared knowledge and organizational learning.
 According to Angel (2006), organizations can perform better with an approach based on the continuum model.
